						               													<description>This is a Rummy based game with several special features.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game consists of 2 sets of cards valued 1 to 10 in each of four colours plus 24 &amp;quot;special&amp;quot; cards. The objective of the game is to get rid of all your cards by creating runs and/or sets (&amp;quot;sets&amp;quot; means either from now on) of at least 3 cards and playing them in front of other players so becoming penalty points that count against those players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are several sorts of Joker that may be used to make up the 3+ cards sets. &amp;quot;Double&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Triple Jokers&amp;quot; double and triple the value of the sets they are in.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are 8 &amp;quot;Pass the set&amp;quot; cards that enable a player to pass any one set in front of them on to another player with the exception of sets containing a &amp;quot;Super Joker&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are 4 &amp;quot;Take it Back&amp;quot; cards that can be used to immediately counter the &amp;quot;Take it Back&amp;quot; cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A deal finishes when any one player succeeds in reducing their hand to zero cards. All players score and record the value of the cards in front of them and in their hand. A game consists of 5 deals, the winner being the player with least penalty points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
